org.eclipse.eef

Interface EEFCheckboxDescription

  • All Superinterfaces:
    EEFControlDescription, EEFWidgetDescription, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    EEFCheckboxDescriptionImpl

    public interface EEFCheckboxDescription
extends EEFWidgetDescription
    A representation of the model object 'EEF Checkbox Description'. Represents a checkbox used to edit a boolean property.

    The following features are supported:

    • Value Expression
    • Edit Expression
    • Style
    • Conditional Styles
    See Also:
    EefPackage.getEEFCheckboxDescription()
